  "texts": [
    "Cloze task.",
    "The Estonian cloze task seems too hard, possibly due to the extremely low resources of Estonian in the Llama-2 training data: Llama-2-7B has a 0% success probability after the last layer.",
    "Interestingly, the Estonian success probability is slightly greater than 0% in the intermediate layers, when the logit lens decodes to English.",
    "The success probability might increase if we included synonyms of the translated words or used human experts for the creation of the cloze examples instead of GPT-4.",
    "We also performed our analysis on Mistral-7B, a model from outside the Llama model family."
  ],
